a solid sequel while not as breathtaking as kurkov 's orginal `` death and the penguin '' , this sequel was still highly amusing and captivating . after viktor abandons his pet penguin to save himself at the end of the last novel , `` penguin lost '' picks up with viktor trying to make ammends for his earlier actions . a great book , but you should read `` death and the penguin '' first , if you want to follow the plot